OL,3,CRSC asks mother and baby to leave
OL,4,Ctheatre after baby disrupts performance
OL,6,FThe Royal Shakespeare Company in
OL,7,FStratford-Upon-Avon asked a mother and
OL,8,Fbaby to leave The Tempest after
OL,9,Faudience members complained about
OL,10,Fnoise.
OL,12,FIt's after a baby was heard "gurgling
OL,13,Fand cooing" in the audience.
OL,15,FThe mother and baby were reportedly
OL,16,Fasked not to return for the second
OL,17,Fpart of the performance after audience
OL,18,Fmembers asked for refunds.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
