SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781175772
OL,3,CRSC asks mother and baby to leave
OL,4,Ctheatre after baby disrupts performance
OL,6,FSir Kenneth Branagh plays the lead
OL,7,Fcharacter Prospero in Shakespeare's
OL,8,Ffinal play and it's the first time
OL,9,Fhe's been at the theatre for 30 years.
OL,11,FIn response, the Royal Shakespeare
OL,12,FCompany told ITV News Central: "It is
OL,13,Fvital that all our audiences feel
OL,14,Fwelcome at our theatres. Our Babes in
OL,15,FArms Policy aims to ensure that
OL,16,Fparents and carers with young babies
OL,17,Fcan enjoy our spaces. Alongside the
OL,18,Fauditoria, we offer alternative areas
OL,19,Fif anyone becomes unsettled during a
OL,20,Fperformance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781175772
OL,3,CRSC asks mother and baby to leave
OL,4,Ctheatre after baby disrupts performance
OL,6,F"Babes in arms (babies from 0-18
OL,7,Fmonths) can be admitted to any
OL,8,Fperformance at the RSC, with the
OL,9,Fexception of preview performances,
OL,10,Ffree of charge. We understand that
OL,11,Fexcessive noise during a performance
OL,12,Fcan be distracting to other audience
OL,13,Fmembers and the actors. Our policy
OL,14,Ftherefore advises that if the baby is
OL,15,Fdisturbing others, an adult from the
OL,16,Fparty may need to watch the show from
OL,17,Fthe screen outside the auditorium with
OL,18,Fthe baby.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
