OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781175772
OL,3,CRSC asks mother and baby to leave
OL,4,Ctheatre after baby disrupts performance
OL,6,F"We encourage people wishing to attend
OL,7,Fa performance with a babe in arms to
OL,8,Fattend one of our chilled
OL,9,Fperformances, as they may find the
OL,10,Fenvironment more relaxing. These
OL,11,Fperformances are particularly suited
OL,12,Fto people who feel more at ease
OL,13,Fknowing they can go in and out of the
OL,14,Fauditorium.
OL,16,F"Our front of house staff undergo
OL,17,Fextensive training to ensure all
OL,18,Faudience members have the best
OL,19,Fexperience possible."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
